query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  projectId,
  pesquisaId,
  CONCAT('projectId=', COALESCE(projectId, 0), ' pesquisaId=', COALESCE(pesquisaId, 0)) as vinculo
FROM mercados_unicos
GROUP BY projectId, pesquisaId
ORDER BY projectId, pesquisaId;
